          {userStation.status}
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
))}
```

### Rule 6.7: Station Management Error Handling
- **ALWAYS** provide specific error messages for station operations
- **ALWAYS** handle network errors gracefully
- **ALWAYS** validate input before making API calls
- **ALWAYS** show user-friendly error messages

```typescript
